FBIS3-58793 "drweu015_p_94003" FBIS-WEU-94-015 Document Type:Daily Report 25 Jan 1994 GREECE Former National Bank Governor Wounded in Athens NC2401091294 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network in Greek 0800 GMT 24 Jan 94 NC2401091294 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network Language: Greek Article Type:BFN [Text] There was an assassination attempt on Mikhail Vranopoulos, former governor of the National Bank, at 0910 today on 46 Solon Street. An unidentified man wearing a suit fired four shots at Vranopoulos, hitting him in the abdomen. The gunfire also wounded an unidentified passerby. After the shooting, the culprit escaped on a motorcycle driven by an accomplice. Mr. Vranopoulos was taken to Evangelismos Hospital.
